from django.test import TestCase

from django.shortcuts import render
from .models import Information

def information_list(request):
    informations = Information.objects.prefetch_related('years', 'semesters', 'affiliation', 'course').all()
    return render(request, 'information/information_list.html', {'informations': informations})
